<subSubSection id="C337088DF765B124B182FD7036A740AF" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F765B124B182FD7033DC408B" blockId="16.[151,1437,547,1509]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F765B124B182FD7032C241E4" box="[199,251,655,681]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: Sundevall in his original description (1850: 100) gives no indication that he had more than a single male at hand. The original type series probably consisted of 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF765B124B2DBFD4C3676418F" box="[926,1103,691,717]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" type="generic">four specimens</specimenCount>
(but Sundevall’s acquisition catalogue is very difficult to read for this species). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F765B124B3BFFD28362041B3" author="Gyldenstolpe, N." box="[762,1049,727,753]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref28755" refString="Gyldenstolpe, N. (1926) Types of birds in the Royal Natural History Museum in Stockholm. Arkiv f or Zoologi, 19, 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1926">Gyldenstolpe (1926: 29)</bibRefCitation>
referred to NRM 568732 [6538] as a “type”, here treated as a 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F765B124B098FD0430704057" box="[477,585,763,789]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation of this adult male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F765B124B569FD0436DC4057" box="[1068,1253,763,789]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" value="1843-10-02">2 October 1843</date>
at Spitskop (1) (Spitzkop) according to the skin label, but Saulspoort according to 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F765B124B2EAFCE036F6407B" author="Gyldenstolpe, N." box="[943,1231,799,825]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" pagination="1 - 116" refId="ref28755" refString="Gyldenstolpe, N. (1926) Types of birds in the Royal Natural History Museum in Stockholm. Arkiv f or Zoologi, 19, 1 - 116." type="journal article" year="1926">Gyldenstolpe (1926: 29)</bibRefCitation>
(see below). The 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF765B124B1D2FCBC33BA401F" box="[151,387,835,861]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" type="generic" typeStatus="paralectotypes">three paralectotypes</specimenCount>
are: NRM 90169719 [6537], a juvenile male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F765B124B54BFCBD36E6401F" box="[1038,1247,834,861]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" value="1843-12-05">5 December 1843</date>
near the Crocodile River; NRM 534116 [6539], a mounted female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F765B124B22EFC99360540C3" box="[875,1084,870,897]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" value="1843-12-05">5 December 1843</date>
near the Crocodile River; and RMNH. 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F765B124B1B3FC74337A40E7" box="[246,323,907,933]" class="Aves" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" phylum="Chordata" rank="class">AVES</taxonomicName>
.123244 [6540], a juvenile male, collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F765B124B27EFC75363740E7" box="[827,1038,906,933]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" value="1843-12-05">5 December 1843</date>
near the Crocodile River, sent on exchange to Leiden in 1850.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B925B06F765B124B182FC2C36A740AF" blockId="16.[151,1437,547,1509]" box="[199,1182,978,1005]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">
<materialsCitation id="3B45515BF765B124B182FC2C36A040AF" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3766756308" box="[199,1177,978,1005]" collectionCode="VERIFIED" latitude="-24.866667" location="Spitskop" longLatPrecision="1249" longitude="26.666666" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="North West" typeStatus="holotype">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F765B124B182FC2C331A40A8" box="[199,291,979,1005]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">VERIFIED</collectionCode>
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F765B124B06FFC25336240A8" box="[298,347,986,1002]" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">TYPE</typeStatus>
LOCALITY: 
<location id="8EF20DDDF765B124B091FC2C300F40AF" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F765B124B1D2FE2532C446A7:8EF20DDDF765B124B091FC2C300F40AF" box="[468,566,979,1005]" latitude="-24.866667" longLatPrecision="1249" longitude="26.666666" name="Spitskop" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" stateProvince="North West">Spitskop</location>
(1) (
<geoCoordinate id="EE193DC1F765B124B328FC2C313C40AF" box="[621,773,978,1005]" degrees="24" direction="south" minutes="52" orientation="latitude" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" precision="925" value="-24.866667">24° 52’ south</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="EE193DC1F765B124B254FC2C31A140AF" box="[785,920,979,1005]" degrees="26" direction="east" minutes="40" orientation="longitude" pageId="16" pageNumber="537" precision="925" value="26.666666">26° 40’ east</geoCoordinate>
), 
<collectingRegion id="49E995E4F765B124B2E9FC2C36A040AF" box="[940,1177,979,1005]" country="Botswana" name="North West" pageId="16" pageNumber="537">North West Province</collectingRegion>
</materialsCitation>
.
